  "texts": [
    "The vortex street consists of a coherent system of vortices whose rotational axes are aligned with the cylinder axis.",
    "This case has been extensively studied both experimentally and numerically, making it suitable for validation and data-driven modeling.The viscous fluid is governed by the incompressible Navier-Stokes equations (NSE), which originate from the conservation of mass and momentum.",
    "Under incompressible and isothermal conditions, the mass conservation reduces to the divergence-free condition of the velocity field, and the energy equation can be neglected.",
    "Let u = (u, v, w) denote the velocity vector.",
    "The NSE in Cartesian coordinates are then given by∇ • u = 0, ∂u ∂t + (u • ∇)u = - 1 ρ ∇p + ν∇ 2 u, (22)where ρ is the fluid density, ν the kinematic viscosity, and p the pressure field."
